|| 1924–1930 ||[[蒙古人民共和国|蒙古人民共和国]]的第一面旗帜。<ref name="selenge">{{cite web|url=http://www.selenge.nso.mn/page/594|title=ТАНИН МЭДЭХҮЙ|agency=National Statistics Office of Mongolia|website=selenge.nso.mn|accessdate=29 November 2018|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919155016/http://www.selenge.nso.mn/page/594|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wsm" /><ref name="drvalfarmer.blogspot.com">{{cite web|url=http://drvalfarmer.blogspot.com/2013/04/wednesday-visit-to-parliament-history.html|title=Musings in Mongolia|last=Farmer|first=Val|department=Mongolian Parliament|date=24 April 2013|accessdate=29 November 2018|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902031130/http://drvalfarmer.blogspot.com/2013/04/wednesday-visit-to-parliament-history.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="markodehaeck.free.fr">{{cite web|url=http://markodehaeck.free.fr/FILLES/MN/MN%20MONGOLIAN%20FLAG%20MUSEUM%203.png|title=Mongolian Statehood History Museum (1)|website=markodehaeck.free.fr|accessdate=29 November 2018|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717131951/http://markodehaeck.free.fr/FILLES/MN/MN%20MONGOLIAN%20FLAG%20MUSEUM%203.png|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://markodehaeck.free.fr/FILLES/MN/MN%201924%20foto.png|title=Mongolian Statehood History Museum (1924 Flag)|website=markodehaeck.free.fr|accessdate=29 November 2018|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717120131/http://markodehaeck.free.fr/FILLES/MN/MN%201924%20foto.png|dead-url=no}}</ref> 正如1924年蒙古宪法所述。<ref name=InnerAsia>{{cite book|title=Inner Asia Volume 9|year=2007|publisher=Global Oriental|url=https://books.google.se/books?redir_esc=y&hl=sv&id=07URAQAAMAAJ&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=mongolia+1924|access-date=2019-09-02|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019115517/https://books.google.se/books?redir_esc=y&hl=sv&id=07URAQAAMAAJ&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=mongolia+1924|dead-url=no}}</ref>  旗帜的确切形状和设计并未完全标准化（仅描述为“旗帜为红色，国徽位于中心”）<ref name=InnerAsia />并且可以看到有关旗帜的文字和形状等的一些变化。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://undesten.mn/75794.html|title=Тусгаар тогтнол чамайг тунхаглан бичнэ би|website=undesten.mn|accessdate=1 January 2019|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227095806/http://undesten.mn/75794.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Nam>{{cite web|url=http://www.nam.mn/a/811|title="МОНГОЛЫН СОНГОДОГ БҮТЭЭЛҮҮД" ҮЗЭСГЭЛЭН НЭЭЛТЭЭ ХИЙЛЭЭ|website=nam.mn|accessdate=16 May 2019|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902031131/http://www.nam.mn/a/811|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=Manjur/>   尽管采用了新的旗帜，但在1930年宪法和旗帜通过之前，国旗仍然保持着在1930年代的使用。<ref name=Manjur>https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/mn/1/14/Mongol-Manjur_border_conference_1937.jpg {{Wayback|url=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/mn/1/14/Mongol-Manjur_border_conference_1937.jpg |date=20190125073512 }} Photo from the Manzhouli conference (1935-1936) which shows the flag of Manchukuo and Mongolia</ref><ref name=Anti>{{cite web|url=https://newspress.mn/uploads/ZP9MGql.jpg|title=Anti-Buddhism poster, 1932|last=Д.Батбаяр|website=newspress.mn|accessdate=1 January 2019|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021075716/https://newspress.mn/uploads/ZP9MGql.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>
